    "rationale": "Credibility assessment accepted for submission purposes under Minimal profile. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or flagged as epistemic gaps with documented rationale. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors not assessed due to data limitations at MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ partially completed. Assessment accepted as complete submission package acknowledging outstanding gaps; regulatory acceptance of the underlying model is not implied.",
